http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/Entrepreneur-training-scheme/article14020688.ece

The Union government’s Science and Technology Department and public consultancy institution Kitco are jointly organising a six-week free entrepreneur training programme for science and engineering graduates in the city in January and February.CertificatesInterested participants should arrive with original certificates proving their age and qualification for an interview scheduled from 10 a.m. to 12.30 p.m. on January 28 at Kitco’s office in Kowdiar in the city.For more information, contact 0471-2728543, 2724462, 9747044209, according to a press release issued here on Monday.